properties.Name: PolicyholderLanguageUsage
properties.Description:
The various uses or applications of the associated Language regarding the Policyholder for the associated period.

Ex:

- Documentation Language = Spanish
- Service Language = Spanish
- Legal Notice Language = English
- Billing Language = Spanish

Columns.Name: LanguageUsageId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of the Language Usage.

Columns.Name: IsoLanguageId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an ISO Language.

Columns.Name: PolicyholderId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Policyholder.

Columns.Name: PeriodStartDate
Columns.Description: The period start date for which the Language Use(s) are defined.

Columns.Name: PeriodEndDate
Columns.Description: The period end date for which the Language Use(s) are defined.

Columns.Name: Note
Columns.Description: Notes, comments or additional information regarding the application of the associated Language for the Policyholder.
